		<title>Who are these PPL?: Five questions, #8</title>
		<link>http://theppl.us/blog/578</link>
		<comments>http://theppl.us/blog/578#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 01:35:43 +0000</pubDate>
